title: Skillfeed Professional Advertisement Design Tutorial In Adobe Il
description:
Skillfeed Professional Advertisement Design Tutorial In Adobe Illustrator CC 2014


In this tutorial you will be learning how to design a flyer that I
created for a local client of mine. In this tutorial you will be
learning how to set up an image in Adobe Photoshop CC 2014 to the
correct color mode and in Adobe Illustrator CC 2014 you will then be
learning how to setup your document build the entire layout and
finalize and save for print purposes
